title: Aftershocks of a Reversal of Roe v. Wade
itunes:title: Aftershocks of a Reversal of Roe v. Wade
description:
June Grasso speaks to Mary Ziegler, a professor at UC Davis Law School, and Elizabeth Sepper, a professor at the University of Texas Law School, about the repercussions of the Supreme Court reversing Roe v. Wade and a woman's constitutional right to abortion.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
